reviews.text:
Very rich and creamy. The toasted almond is blatant and delicious. Took a look at the ingredients, and WOW. I did not know I liked pistachio. That would be the other nuttiness I couldn't place. The dab o honey from milk and honey is a great touch.&#xD;
&#xD;
Gave the rest of my sample to a friend who can't vape hardly anything but killed  1/4 of my tank in a 10 minute break. Very smooth. Winner here.
